{"tid":896416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《假如愛有天意》真人版！50年前因移民錯過愛情！發生在1968年尖沙咀餅店的真實愛情故事！","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"355bb613eb0ae60622164c9c254d491fb7f3864e","tid":896416,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"無法開花結果的愛情，總會成為人最深刻難忘的經歷。今次訴說的愛情故事，是發生在香港50年前的真人真事。女主角Nancy Wong（當年名為Lance Tam）的女兒Selina Wong 近日在Facebook發起尋人啟事，希望為白髮蒼蒼的媽媽尋回年輕時一段愛情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/real-love-story-lance-danny/2721042-1-chi-HK/50-1968_img_750_h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Freal-love-story-lance-danny%2F2721042-1-chi-HK%2F50-1968_img_750_h.png&h=a41503f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/real-love-story-lence-danny/screen-shot-2018-11-08-at-3-10-47-pm/2721073-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2018-11-08-At-3-10-47-PM_img_750_h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Freal-love-story-lence-danny%2Fscreen-shot-2018-11-08-at-3-10-47-pm%2F2721073-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2018-11-08-At-3-10-47-PM_img_750_h.png&h=49daed79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事發生在1968年尖沙咀加拿分道麗琪餅店，女主角Lance年僅20歲，在餅店裡工作。一名18歲年輕小伙子Danny（全名為𧝁永釗 ）每日在這間餅店幫襯，原因只有一個：為了Lance。他經常接Lance下班，更親自送她回上水的家，有次更騎著電單車接送<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/real-love-story-lence-danny/screen-shot-2018-11-08-at-3-10-52-pm/2721082-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2018-11-08-At-3-10-52-PM_img_750_h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Freal-love-story-lence-danny%2Fscreen-shot-2018-11-08-at-3-10-52-pm%2F2721082-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2018-11-08-At-3-10-52-PM_img_750_h.png&h=816075da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人只相識了大約6個月，深知對方的情意，可惜還未來得及表白，Lance便要舉家移民英國。得知情況的Danny只能撰寫情書道「I love you forever, and I will never change my mind, never!」更附上自己的照片、出生日期（1949年12月10日出生）及中文名字「𧝁永釗」，相信Danny 當時始終認為，兩人會再次相見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/real-love-story-lence-danny/danny/2721100-1-chi-HK/Danny_img_750_h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Freal-love-story-lence-danny%2Fdanny%2F2721100-1-chi-HK%2FDanny_img_750_h.png&h=23c5b4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一別50年，當年這段尚在萌芽的愛情又再被翻出來。女兒Selina Wong指，如今媽媽只為跟Danny重聚。讓闊別50年的老人重拾當年回憶，確實令人感動！你認識𧝁永釗Danny嗎？數數手指，他如今應是68歲的老人了。如果認識，快跟Selina Wong吧！（電郵：[url]sky_wong88@hotmail.com[/url] ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mxLAlGWQ4pM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmxLAlGWQ4pM&d=gKsu5e2IlVg3nxeHSNKNb%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=26a21b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mxLAlGWQ4pM</a>"}]}